description:
Arnott’s Shapes Originals are an Aussie favourite savoury biscuit snack. Arnott’s Shapes Original Savoury offer a rich flavour combination of sweet and salty on a crisp and crunchy cracker base. Oven baked, not fried, and foil-wrapped for freshness.

Arnott’s Shapes Originals are big on crunch and even bigger on taste – and perfect for any occasion! These sweet and salty biscuits are oven-baked crackers with loads of flavour you can see, and no artificial colours or preservatives. Whether you’re sharing with friends at the park or looking for a fun afternoon snack with flavours that your whole family will love, Arnott’s Shapes Original Savoury biscuits are the perfect flavoured cracker. Foil-wrapped for freshness, these sweet and salty crackers are a go-to savoury cravings-buster for any occasion. Bags of flavour in every box, no matter which flavour you savour!

A rich flavour combination of sweet and salty on a crisp and crunchy cracker base.

Flavour you can see.

Foil-wrapped for freshness.

Oven baked, not fried.

Made in Australia.
name: Arnott's Shapes Crackers Biscuits Savoury 185G
